headline: The Cooper Companies (COO) Moved Higher as Multiple Tailwinds Align
summary: Sustainable Growth Advisers (SGA), an investment management company, released its fourth-quarter investor letter for its “U.S. Large Cap Growth Strategy.” A copy of the letter can be downloaded here. In Q4 2025, the Portfolio returned 0.3% (Gross) and 0.2% (Net) compared to 1.1% return for the Russell 1000 Growth Index and 2.7% gain for the S&P 500 […]
